Key Match Events: Alperen Şengün delivered a solid performance with 16 points, 5 rebounds, 4 assists, 2 blocks, and 1 steal in 24 minutes of action.
Jalen Green and Fred VanVleet also contributed significantly, each adding 21 points.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The Houston Rockets cruised to a dominant 127-100 victory over the San Antonio Spurs, securing their fifth win of the season.
Others: On the losing side, the Spurs' Victor Wembanyama scored 15 points and grabbed 6 rebounds, while Julian Champagnie posted 13 points and 3 boards.
